In [43]:
penguinsFixed = penguins.fillna(0)
In [44]:
features = ['bill_length_mm','bill_depth_mm','flipper_length_mm', 'body_mass_g']
km = KMeans(n_clusters=4, random_state=43).fit(penguinsFixed[features])
In [45]:
penguinsFixed['cluster'] = km.predict(penguinsFixed[features])
